Comedy series about an out-of-work musician who forges an unlikely alliance with his 12-year-old nephew after being morally blackmailed into looking after him by his chaotic sister.
 
 
 
1/6 Andy finds new purpose in his life when he becomes the unlikely charge of nephew Errol 
 
2/6 Andy persuades Errol that, for many reasons, he should go to Alfie's birthday party. 

3/6 Andy holds auditions for his new band so he can enter the Battle of the Bands competition.
 
4/6 Errol's grandmother Joan is hosting a family lunch and Sam ropes Andy into coming along. 
 
5/6 Andy is trying to break up with Shelly, make up with Gwen and woo Errol's teacher Melodie.  
 
6/6 Andy and Errol are offered the opportunity to sign with Rage Records and producer Mo Kahn.
